+Once we know the fault, we quote you the repair cost. Because we've done this over 15,000 times, we know exactly what each repair entails and how long it takes.
+
+If it's a **charging port issue**, we clean and realign the connector, or replace it if necessary. This typically resolves within 24 hours.
+
+If the **battery is dead**, we replace it. We use genuine Apple batteries or equivalent quality components. Turnaround is 2-3 business days because we test thoroughly before releasing the machine.
+
