+    content: `# MacBook Pro M3 GPU Fault Repair: What It Costs, Turnaround, and How We Handle It
+
+The integrated GPU on your M3-powered MacBook Pro is engineered to handle everything from creative workflows to demanding gaming sessions. When it fails, the ripple effect across your machine can be severe: graphical glitches during editing, kernel panics during rendering, or complete display blackouts. Over the past five years, we have serviced more than 18,000 MacBooks at our Hyde Park workshop, and M3 GPU faults represent a growing proportion of our repair intake, particularly as these machines edge toward their second and third year of ownership.
