+
+## Understanding M3 GPU Faults and Early Warning Signs
+
+The GPU in the M3 MacBook Pro comprises between 8 and 10 cores, depending on your configuration. These cores handle graphics rendering, machine learning acceleration, and display output. When faults develop, symptoms often appear in clusters: your external monitor flickers or fails to detect; your Timeline in Final Cut Pro becomes sluggish; or your display kernel panics repeatedly.
