+
+The M3 SoC itself cannot be replaced in isolation. Instead, repair requires either full logic-board replacement (the costliest option) or, in specific scenarios, microsoldering repair of the GPU fabric or supporting power delivery circuits, a technique our technicians have refined across more than 8,000 similar repairs.
