+    content: `# MacBook Pro M3 Logic Board Repair: What It Costs and How Long It Takes in Johannesburg
+
+If your MacBook Pro M3 has stopped turning on, won't charge, or shows the dreaded kernel panic loop, the logic board is often the culprit. We have seen a sharp rise in M3 logic board failures over the past 18 months at our Hyde Park workshop, some caused by manufacturing defects, others by liquid damage or power surges during load shedding. The good news is that logic board repair is almost always possible, and considerably cheaper than replacing the entire machine.
