+When your MacBook Pro M3 refuses to power up, the panic is real. You've got work waiting, deadlines looming, and suddenly your most essential device is a useless aluminium rectangle. We've seen this scenario play out hundreds of times in our Hyde Park Johannesburg workshop, and the good news is that "won't turn on" rarely means your machine is beyond saving.
